Sentencas: Solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC) were fabricated with gadolinia-doped ceria (GDC)-yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ), thin bi-layer electrolytes supported on Ni+YSZ anodes.
Titulo: Measurement of oxygen chemical potential in Gd2O3-doped ceria-Y2O3-stabilized zirconia bi-layer electrolyte, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The GDC and YSZ layer thicknesses were 45 mu m, and similar to 5 mu m, respectively.
Titulo: Measurement of oxygen chemical potential in Gd2O3-doped ceria-Y2O3-stabilized zirconia bi-layer electrolyte, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Two types of cells were made; YSZ layer between anode and GDC (GDC/YSZ) and YSZ layer between cathode and GDC (YSZ/GDC).
Titulo: Measurement of oxygen chemical potential in Gd2O3-doped ceria-Y2O3-stabilized zirconia bi-layer electrolyte, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Two platinum reference electrodes were embedded within the GDC layer.
Titulo: Measurement of oxygen chemical potential in Gd2O3-doped ceria-Y2O3-stabilized zirconia bi-layer electrolyte, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Cells were tested at 650 degrees C with hydrogen as fuel and air as oxidant.
Titulo: Measurement of oxygen chemical potential in Gd2O3-doped ceria-Y2O3-stabilized zirconia bi-layer electrolyte, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Electric potentials between embedded reference electrodes and anode and between cathode and anode were measured at open circuit.
Titulo: Measurement of oxygen chemical potential in Gd2O3-doped ceria-Y2O3-stabilized zirconia bi-layer electrolyte, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells
Measurement of oxygen chemical potential in Gd2O3-doped ceria-Y2O3-stabilized zirconia bi-layer electrolyte, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electric potential was nearly constant through GDC in the cathode/YSZ/GDC/anode cells.
Titulo: Measurement of oxygen chemical potential in Gd2O3-doped ceria-Y2O3-stabilized zirconia bi-layer electrolyte, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: By contrast, it varied monotonically through GDC in the cathode/GDC/YSZ/anode cells.
Titulo: Measurement of oxygen chemical potential in Gd2O3-doped ceria-Y2O3-stabilized zirconia bi-layer electrolyte, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Estimates of oxygen chemical potential, mu(O2), variation through GDC were made.
Titulo: Measurement of oxygen chemical potential in Gd2O3-doped ceria-Y2O3-stabilized zirconia bi-layer electrolyte, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: mu(O2) within the GDC layer in the cathode/GDC/YSZ/anode cell decreased as the current was increased.
Titulo: Measurement of oxygen chemical potential in Gd2O3-doped ceria-Y2O3-stabilized zirconia bi-layer electrolyte, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: By contrast, mu(O2) within the GDC layer in the cathode/YSZ/GDC/anode cell increased as the cutrent was increased.
Titulo: Measurement of oxygen chemical potential in Gd2O3-doped ceria-Y2O3-stabilized zirconia bi-layer electrolyte, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The cathode/YSZ/GDC/anode cell exhibited maximum power density of similar to 0.52 W cm(-2) at 650 degrees C while the cathode/GDC/YSZ/anode cell exhibited maximum power density of similar to 0.14 W cm(-2) for the same total electrolyte thickness.
